en away my judgment.","year":-1520},{"id":"recwpChPP6A0aGLSG","ref":"Job.34.6","text":"Should I lie against my right? my wound is incurable without transgression.","year":-1520},{"id":"recpTVi0Wlos0bnPL","ref":"Job.34.7","text":"What man is like Job, who drinketh up scorning like water?","year":-1520},{"id":"rec9XJL1a3C76YYsF","ref":"Job.34.8","text":"Which goeth in company with the workers of iniquity, and walketh with wicked men.","year":-1520}]}
